metadata.name: Santo Amaro Sunset
metadata.subtitle: Wonderful May Sunset at Santo Amaro, Brazil
metadata.title: Santo Amaro Sunset
metadata.description:
One of the most wonderful experiences in life

Santo Amaro is located inside Parque Nacional dos Lençois Maranhenses, the most iconic Brazilian desert with 600 square miles (1,550 km²) of bright white sand and 36.000+ large seasonal rain ponds.

This photograph shows the actual dusk sky colors of May.
